task.summary:
Pretty much finished it all. It can git clone, setup, and create the files for a new lab. It can also push them to clac, where I can run the submit script. It can also parse the instructions to determine the lab number and number of parts.
isFunction() from isType had to be changed. Object.prototype.toString.call() returns "[object Function]" for a function, but "[object AsyncFunction]" for an async function. So I had to use typeof o === "function" instead.
Using rsync instead of scp now. Makefile also includes pull and push rules for syncing using rsync.
Added lab submission directory to gitignore.
